116 bool MotionPlanningFrame::computeCartesianPlan()
117 {
118  ros::WallTime start = ros::WallTime::now();
119  // get goal pose
120  moveit::core::RobotState goal = *planning_display_->getQueryGoalState();
121  std::vector<geometry_msgs::Pose> waypoints;
122  const std::string& link_name = move_group_->getEndEffectorLink();
123  const moveit::core::LinkModel* link = move_group_->getRobotModel()->getLinkModel(link_name);
124  if (!link)
125  {
126  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Failed to determine unique end-effector link: " << link_name);
127  return false;
128  }
129  waypoints.push_back(tf2::toMsg(goal.getGlobalLinkTransform(link)));
130 
131  // setup default params
132  double cart_step_size = 0.01;
133  double cart_jump_thresh = 0.0;
134  bool avoid_collisions = true;
135 
136  // compute trajectory
137  moveit_msgs::RobotTrajectory trajectory;
138  double fraction =
139  move_group_->computeCartesianPath(waypoints, cart_step_size, cart_jump_thresh, trajectory, avoid_collisions);
140 
141  if (fraction >= 1.0)
142  {
143  ROS_INFO("Achieved %f %% of Cartesian path", fraction * 100.);
144 
145  // Compute time parameterization to also provide velocities
146  // https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/moveit-users/MOoFxy2exT4
147  robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory rt(move_group_->getRobotModel(), move_group_->getName());
148  rt.setRobotTrajectoryMsg(*move_group_->getCurrentState(), trajectory);
149  trajectory_processing::IterativeParabolicTimeParameterization iptp;
150  bool success =
151  iptp.computeTimeStamps(rt, ui_->velocity_scaling_factor->value(), ui_->acceleration_scaling_factor->value());
152  ROS_INFO("Computing time stamps %s", success ? "SUCCEDED" : "FAILED");
153 
154  // Store trajectory in current_plan_
155  current_plan_ = std::make_shared<moveit::planning_interface::MoveGroupInterface::Plan>();
156  rt.getRobotTrajectoryMsg(current_plan_->trajectory_);
157  current_plan_->planning_time_ = (ros::WallTime::now() - start).toSec();
158  return success;
159  }
160  return false;
161 }

163 bool MotionPlanningFrame::computeJointSpacePlan()
164 {
165  current_plan_ = std::make_shared<moveit::planning_interface::MoveGroupInterface::Plan>();
166  return move_group_->plan(*current_plan_) == moveit::planning_interface::MoveItErrorCode::SUCCESS;
167 }

169 void MotionPlanningFrame::computePlanButtonClicked()
170 {
171  if (!move_group_)
172  return;
173 
174  // Clear status
175  ui_->result_label->setText("Planning...");
176 
177  configureForPlanning();
178  planning_display_->rememberPreviousStartState();
179  bool success = (ui_->use_cartesian_path->isEnabled() && ui_->use_cartesian_path->checkState()) ?
180  computeCartesianPlan() :
181  computeJointSpacePlan();
182 
183  if (success)
184  {
185  ui_->execute_button->setEnabled(true);
186  ui_->result_label->setText(QString("Time: ").append(QString::number(current_plan_->planning_time_, 'f', 3)));
187  }
188  else
189  {
190  current_plan_.reset();
191  ui_->result_label->setText("Failed");
192  }
193  Q_EMIT planningFinished();
194 }

196 void MotionPlanningFrame::computeExecuteButtonClicked()
197 {
198  // ensures the MoveGroupInterface is not destroyed while executing
199  moveit::planning_interface::MoveGroupInterfacePtr mgi(move_group_);
200  if (mgi && current_plan_)
201  {
202  ui_->stop_button->setEnabled(true); // enable stopping
203  bool success = mgi->execute(*current_plan_) == moveit::planning_interface::MoveItErrorCode::SUCCESS;
204  onFinishedExecution(success);
205  }
206 }

208 void MotionPlanningFrame::computePlanAndExecuteButtonClicked()
209 {
210  if (!move_group_)
211  return;
212  configureForPlanning();
213  planning_display_->rememberPreviousStartState();
214  // move_group::move() on the server side, will always start from the current state
215  // to suppress a warning, we pass an empty state (which encodes "start from current state")
216  move_group_->setStartStateToCurrentState();
217  ui_->stop_button->setEnabled(true);
218  if (ui_->use_cartesian_path->isEnabled() && ui_->use_cartesian_path->checkState())
219  {
220  if (computeCartesianPlan())
221  computeExecuteButtonClicked();
222  }
223  else
224  {
225  bool success = move_group_->move() == moveit::planning_interface::MoveItErrorCode::SUCCESS;
226  onFinishedExecution(success);
227  }
228  ui_->plan_and_execute_button->setEnabled(true);
229 }

237 void MotionPlanningFrame::onFinishedExecution(bool success)
238 {
239  // visualize result of execution
240  if (success)
241  ui_->result_label->setText("Executed");
242  else
243  ui_->result_label->setText(!ui_->stop_button->isEnabled() ? "Stopped" : "Failed");
244  // disable stop button
245  ui_->stop_button->setEnabled(false);
246 
247  // update query start state to current if neccessary
248  if (ui_->start_state_combo_box->currentText() == "<current>")
249  startStateTextChanged(ui_->start_state_combo_box->currentText());
250 
251  // auto-update goal to stored previous state (but only on success)
252  // on failure, the user must update the goal to the previous state himself
253  if (ui_->goal_state_combo_box->currentText() == "<previous>")
254  goalStateTextChanged(ui_->goal_state_combo_box->currentText());
255 }

266  planning_display_->setQueryGoalState(current);

303 void MotionPlanningFrame::updateQueryStateHelper(moveit::core::RobotState& state, const std::string& v)
304 {
305  if (v == "<random>")
306  {
307  configureWorkspace();
308  if (const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg =
309  state.getJointModelGroup(planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup()))
310  state.setToRandomPositions(jmg);
311  return;
312  }
313 
314  if (v == "<random valid>")
315  {
316  configureWorkspace();
317 
318  if (const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg =
319  state.getJointModelGroup(planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup()))
320  {
321  // Loop until a collision free state is found
322  static const int MAX_ATTEMPTS = 100;
323  int attempt_count = 0; // prevent loop for going forever
324  while (attempt_count < MAX_ATTEMPTS)
325  {
326  // Generate random state
327  state.setToRandomPositions(jmg);
328 
329  state.update(); // prevent dirty transforms
330 
331  // Test for collision
332  if (planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRO()->isStateValid(state, "", false))
333  break;
334 
335  attempt_count++;
336  }
337  // Explain if no valid rand state found
338  if (attempt_count >= MAX_ATTEMPTS)
339  ROS_WARN("Unable to find a random collision free configuration after %d attempts", MAX_ATTEMPTS);
340  }
341  else
342  {
343  ROS_WARN_STREAM("Unable to get joint model group " << planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup());
344  }
345  return;
346  }
347 
348  if (v == "<current>")
349  {
350  planning_display_->waitForCurrentRobotState();
351  const planning_scene_monitor::LockedPlanningSceneRO& ps = planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRO();
352  if (ps)
353  state = ps->getCurrentState();
354  return;
355  }
356 
357  if (v == "<same as goal>")
358  {
359  state = *planning_display_->getQueryGoalState();
360  return;
361  }
362 
363  if (v == "<same as start>")
364  {
365  state = *planning_display_->getQueryStartState();
366  return;
367  }
368 
369  if (v == "<previous>")
370  {
371  state = planning_display_->getPreviousState();
372  return;
373  }
374 
375  // maybe it is a named state
376  if (const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg = state.getJointModelGroup(planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup()))
377  state.setToDefaultValues(jmg, v);
378 }

380 void MotionPlanningFrame::populatePlannersList(const std::vector<moveit_msgs::PlannerInterfaceDescription>& desc)
381 {
382  ui_->planning_pipeline_combo_box->clear();
383 
384  planner_descriptions_ = desc;
385  size_t default_planner_index = 0;
386  for (auto& d : planner_descriptions_)
387  {
388  QString item_text(d.pipeline_id.c_str());
389  // Check for default planning pipeline
390  if (d.pipeline_id == default_planning_pipeline_)
391  {
392  if (item_text.isEmpty())
393  item_text = QString::fromStdString(d.name);
394  default_planner_index = ui_->planning_pipeline_combo_box->count();
395  }
396  ui_->planning_pipeline_combo_box->addItem(item_text);
397  }
398  QFont font;
399  font.setBold(true);
400  ui_->planning_pipeline_combo_box->setItemData(default_planner_index, font, Qt::FontRole);
401 
402  // Select default pipeline - triggers populatePlannerDescription() via callback
403  if (!planner_descriptions_.empty())
404  ui_->planning_pipeline_combo_box->setCurrentIndex(default_planner_index);
405 }

407 void MotionPlanningFrame::populatePlannerDescription(const moveit_msgs::PlannerInterfaceDescription& desc)
408 {
409  std::string group = planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup();
410  ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->clear();
411 
412  // set the label for the planning library
413  ui_->library_label->setText(QString::fromStdString(desc.name));
414  ui_->library_label->setStyleSheet("QLabel { color : green; font: bold }");
415 
416  bool found_group = false;
417  // the name of a planner is either "GROUP[planner_id]" or "planner_id"
418  if (!group.empty())
419  {
420  for (const std::string& planner_id : desc.planner_ids)
421  if (planner_id == group)
422  found_group = true;
423  else if (planner_id.substr(0, group.length()) == group)
424  {
425  if (planner_id.size() > group.length() && planner_id[group.length()] == '[')
426  {
427  std::string id = planner_id.substr(group.length());
428  if (id.size() > 2)
429  {
430  id.resize(id.length() - 1);
431  ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->addItem(QString::fromStdString(id.substr(1)));
432  }
433  }
434  }
435  }
436  if (ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->count() == 0 && !found_group)
437  for (const std::string& planner_id : desc.planner_ids)
438  ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->addItem(QString::fromStdString(planner_id));
439 
440  ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->insertItem(0, "<unspecified>");
441 
442  // retrieve default planner config from parameter server
443  const std::string& default_planner_config = move_group_->getDefaultPlannerId(found_group ? group : std::string());
444  int default_index = ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->findText(QString::fromStdString(default_planner_config));
445  if (default_index < 0)
446  default_index = 0; // 0 is <unspecified> fallback
447  ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->setCurrentIndex(default_index);
448 
449  QFont font;
450  font.setBold(true);
451  ui_->planning_algorithm_combo_box->setItemData(default_index, font, Qt::FontRole);
452 }

469 void MotionPlanningFrame::constructPlanningRequest(moveit_msgs::MotionPlanRequest& mreq)
470 {
471  mreq.group_name = planning_display_->getCurrentPlanningGroup();
472  mreq.num_planning_attempts = ui_->planning_attempts->value();
473  mreq.allowed_planning_time = ui_->planning_time->value();
474  mreq.max_velocity_scaling_factor = ui_->velocity_scaling_factor->value();
475  mreq.max_acceleration_scaling_factor = ui_->acceleration_scaling_factor->value();
476  moveit::core::robotStateToRobotStateMsg(*planning_display_->getQueryStartState(), mreq.start_state);
477  mreq.workspace_parameters.min_corner.x = ui_->wcenter_x->value() - ui_->wsize_x->value() / 2.0;
478  mreq.workspace_parameters.min_corner.y = ui_->wcenter_y->value() - ui_->wsize_y->value() / 2.0;
479  mreq.workspace_parameters.min_corner.z = ui_->wcenter_z->value() - ui_->wsize_z->value() / 2.0;
480  mreq.workspace_parameters.max_corner.x = ui_->wcenter_x->value() + ui_->wsize_x->value() / 2.0;
481  mreq.workspace_parameters.max_corner.y = ui_->wcenter_y->value() + ui_->wsize_y->value() / 2.0;
482  mreq.workspace_parameters.max_corner.z = ui_->wcenter_z->value() + ui_->wsize_z->value() / 2.0;
483  moveit::core::RobotStateConstPtr s = planning_display_->getQueryGoalState();
484  const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg = s->getJointModelGroup(mreq.group_name);
485  if (jmg)
486  {
487  mreq.goal_constraints.resize(1);
488  mreq.goal_constraints[0] = kinematic_constraints::constructGoalConstraints(*s, jmg);
489  }
490 }

492 void MotionPlanningFrame::configureWorkspace()
493 {
494  moveit::core::VariableBounds bx, by, bz;
495  bx.position_bounded_ = by.position_bounded_ = bz.position_bounded_ = true;
496 
497  moveit::core::JointModel::Bounds b(3);
498  bx.min_position_ = ui_->wcenter_x->value() - ui_->wsize_x->value() / 2.0;
499  bx.max_position_ = ui_->wcenter_x->value() + ui_->wsize_x->value() / 2.0;
500  by.min_position_ = ui_->wcenter_y->value() - ui_->wsize_y->value() / 2.0;
501  by.max_position_ = ui_->wcenter_y->value() + ui_->wsize_y->value() / 2.0;
502  bz.min_position_ = ui_->wcenter_z->value() - ui_->wsize_z->value() / 2.0;
503  bz.max_position_ = ui_->wcenter_z->value() + ui_->wsize_z->value() / 2.0;
504 
505  if (move_group_)
506  move_group_->setWorkspace(bx.min_position_, by.min_position_, bz.min_position_, bx.max_position_, by.max_position_,
507  bz.max_position_);
508  planning_scene_monitor::PlanningSceneMonitorPtr psm = planning_display_->getPlanningSceneMonitor();
509  // get non-const access to the robot_model and update planar & floating joints as indicated by the workspace settings
510  if (psm && psm->getRobotModelLoader() && psm->getRobotModelLoader()->getModel())
511  {
512  const moveit::core::RobotModelPtr& robot_model = psm->getRobotModelLoader()->getModel();
513  const std::vector<moveit::core::JointModel*>& jm = robot_model->getJointModels();
514  for (moveit::core::JointModel* joint : jm)
515  if (joint->getType() == moveit::core::JointModel::PLANAR)
516  {
517  joint->setVariableBounds(joint->getName() + "/" + joint->getLocalVariableNames()[0], bx);
518  joint->setVariableBounds(joint->getName() + "/" + joint->getLocalVariableNames()[1], by);
519  }
520  else if (joint->getType() == moveit::core::JointModel::FLOATING)
521  {
522  joint->setVariableBounds(joint->getName() + "/" + joint->getLocalVariableNames()[0], bx);
523  joint->setVariableBounds(joint->getName() + "/" + joint->getLocalVariableNames()[1], by);
524  joint->setVariableBounds(joint->getName() + "/" + joint->getLocalVariableNames()[2], bz);
525  }
526  }
527 }

529 void MotionPlanningFrame::configureForPlanning()
530 {
531  move_group_->setStartState(*planning_display_->getQueryStartState());
532  move_group_->setJointValueTarget(*planning_display_->getQueryGoalState());
533  move_group_->setPlanningTime(ui_->planning_time->value());
534  move_group_->setNumPlanningAttempts(ui_->planning_attempts->value());
535  move_group_->setMaxVelocityScalingFactor(ui_->velocity_scaling_factor->value());
536  move_group_->setMaxAccelerationScalingFactor(ui_->acceleration_scaling_factor->value());
537  configureWorkspace();
538  if (static_cast<bool>(planning_display_))
539  planning_display_->dropVisualizedTrajectory();
540 }

585 void MotionPlanningFrame::remoteUpdateCustomStartStateCallback(const moveit_msgs::RobotStateConstPtr& msg)
586 {
587  moveit_msgs::RobotState msg_no_attached(*msg);

599  }
600  }
